\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The South Africa College of Applied Psychology \'28SACAP\'29 is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution is currently offering a Diploma in Counselling Communication and a Graduate Diploma in Counselling.\line \line The Higher Certificate in Counselling and Communication Skills was tabled at the Accreditation Committee of 05 and 06 October and the decision was to defer the programme for the following reason\'3A\line \line The institution should provide details regarding the proposed distance education mode of delivery. In particular it should indicate how teaching and learning material will be adapted to the distance education mode of delivery\'2C how face-to-face contact\'2C if any\'2C will be organised\'2C how practicals will be conducted\'2C how assessment is conducted for distance mode\'2C how library and IT resources would be made available to students and how the teaching and learning strategy will be adapted to cater for the needs of distance education students. Distance Education principles need to be used for all policies. \line \line The institution submitted additional information.\line \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
